    "summary": "Problem: Sep revenue $1,096,384 vs target $1,177,243 — shortfall $80,859. Root cause: No standardized quote-to-order follow-up process / accountability in HP sales team. Countermeasures: create SW on follow-up (C) · 3-Touch Rule for open quotes · align rep hours to account time zones (G) · train on SW (G) · convert quote doc to LSW (G) · daily quote-process check-ins. Status: mixed C/G, still executing."
  },
